Dependencies:
	geph-binder needs libsodium-dev and libgeoip-dev packages to build, and
	geoip-database to execute.

Install build dependencies:
	sudo apt install libsodium-dev libgeoip-dev

Install runtime dependencies:
	sudo apt install geoip-database

Cross Compiling:
	set GOOS and GOARCH, for example, to build geph-client executable for Windows x64:
	GOOS=windows GOARCH=amd64 make geph-client
